USA: Negotiated sales total $681 mln for Aug 21.Negotiated sales total $681 mln for Aug 21.Scheduled negotiated sales total $681 million in 25 offerings for Wednesday, August 21, according to Reuters Municipal Bond Information Group.The largest issue is a $141 million Jersey City, N.J., bond offering through Merrill Lynch & Co.Also on tap is a $100 million Duke University commercial paper offering through BT Securities.Possible sales total $393 million in 3 offerings, including an Intermountain Power Authority $371 million fowards issue through Goldman Sachs & Co.--U.S. Municipal Desk, 212-859-1650